comments: Trent Jr. (POR) makes marginal contact with a bent forearm to VanVleet's (TOR) side and slides it off defending his drive to the basket.
Anthony (POR) hedges the pick and makes marginal contact to VanVleet (TOR) as he absorbs the contact.
Lillard (POR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Trent Jr. (POR) makes lower body contact with Boucher (TOR) that affects his jump shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) makes marginal contact as he moves alongside of Lillard's (POR) drive to the basket and he does not cause him to lose control of the ball.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Lillard (POR) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Covington (POR) makes contact with the ball and dislodges the ball at the end of Siakam's (TOR) drive. Any ensuing contact is deemed incidental.
Lowry (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in McCollum's (POR) path and absorbs the contact.
Trent Jr. (POR) and Lowry (TOR) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
VanVleet (TOR) makes marginal contact to Lillard (POR) defending his drive to the basket.
Lowry (TOR) goes through Lillard (POR) at the end of his drive as he makes the pass and the contact dislodges him from his legally obtained position.
Covington (POR) makes marginal contact with Siakam's (TOR) non-shooting arm as he retreats his arm to a vertical position and the contact does not affect his shot attempt.
Trent Jr. (POR) makes marginal contact to Siakam (TOR) as they engage for the loose ball.
